# Trivy ignore file
# List CVE IDs that have been reviewed and accepted as false positives or not
# applicable to this deployment context.
# Format: one CVE-ID per line, optionally with an inline comment.
#
# Review process: any addition must include the date reviewed, the upstream
# package, and a one-line justification. Re-audit quarterly — if the
# upstream image rebuilds with the fixed package version, remove the entry.

# ── HIGH-severity CVEs inherited from mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/aspnet:8.0 ──
# All five fixes are present in upstream Debian 12 (bookworm-security) but
# the Microsoft base image has not yet been rebuilt against the patched
# packages. We do not run apt-get upgrade inside our build to avoid
# divergence from Microsoft's curated layers. Tracked for re-evaluation
# whenever the base image is rebuilt — Dependabot raises the rebase PR.
CVE-2026-0861    # Reviewed 2026-05-17: libc-bin / libc6 — glibc 2.36-9+deb12u14 pending Microsoft image rebuild
CVE-2026-4878    # Reviewed 2026-05-17: libcap2 — 1:2.66-4+deb12u3 pending Microsoft image rebuild
CVE-2026-29111   # Reviewed 2026-05-17: libsystemd0 / libudev1 — 252.39-1~deb12u2 pending Microsoft image rebuild

# libgnutls30 CVEs disclosed late May / early June 2026. All five fixed
# in 3.7.9-2+deb12u7 but Microsoft has not yet republished
# mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/aspnet:8.0 with the patched package. Tracked
# for removal when Dependabot proposes the next docker-base rebump PR.
CVE-2026-33845   # Reviewed 2026-06-03: libgnutls30 CRITICAL — fix 3.7.9-2+deb12u7 pending Microsoft image rebuild
CVE-2026-42010   # Reviewed 2026-06-03: libgnutls30 CRITICAL — fix 3.7.9-2+deb12u7 pending Microsoft image rebuild
CVE-2026-33846   # Reviewed 2026-06-03: libgnutls30 HIGH — fix 3.7.9-2+deb12u7 pending Microsoft image rebuild
CVE-2026-3833    # Reviewed 2026-06-03: libgnutls30 HIGH — fix 3.7.9-2+deb12u7 pending Microsoft image rebuild
CVE-2026-42009   # Reviewed 2026-06-03: libgnutls30 HIGH — fix 3.7.9-2+deb12u7 pending Microsoft image rebuild
